埋埋"},{"pid":"eea9d959309f763591706985617959b9201fcfc6","tid":439941,"uid":3261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>朋友係你最好依靠嚟<br />\n以前都唔覺，但如果你生活/情感上有咗重大變化之後，朋友就係心靈支撐嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當然要搵知交好難，多啲disclose自己可能會搵到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔就係成日收收埋埋</blockquote><br />\n自問自己性格都癲癲地，都算放，但真心朋友都係嗰幾個，對住佢哋唔會累<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一對住啲hi bye friend 真係心很累，刻意討好人，雖不知你係唔被討好嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e239faf1d166b2a7fe5c54e01443f0b969b44abb","tid":439941,"uid":89998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T20:08:47.000Z","msg":"完全明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對住啲可以暢所欲言的朋友真係好自在<br />\n<br />\n想問樓主 點有機心法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}